('modified', '2007-08-18 23:42:00', '', '<h3>Common cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Berserker cost raised by 1, his overall attack lowered by 1</li>\r\n	<li>Black market reworked. Now costs 7/7/7 and has two modes. In first mode it will switch your cards that are on even positions with opponents cards that are on odd positions. Mode2 - vice versa</li>\r\n	<li>Magic well cost now 8B and 8G, but gives +10 Gems</li>\r\n	<li>Preparations cost now 8B and 8R, but gives +10 Recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Searing fire added: Tower: -2, Wall: -5, Enemy Tower: -2 and Enemy wall: -5</li>\r\n	<li>Stone gargoyle cost raised by 1, Enemy tower: -7, not -8</li>\r\n	<li>Tribute reworked. Now costs 6/6/6 and has two modes. In first mode it will discard your cards that are on even positions and opponents cards that are on odd positions. Mode2 - vice versa</li>\r\n	<li>Wind cost raised to 4/4/4</li>\r\n	<li>Prayer now summons <b>Holy</b> cards</li>\r\n	<li>Draft now summons <b>Soldier</b> cards</li>\r\n	<li>Mage guild now summons <b>Mage cards</b></li>\r\n	<li>School of nature magic now summons <b>Nature</b> spells</li>\r\n	<li>School of restoration now summons <b>Destruction</b> spells</li>\r\n	<li>Necromancy lost play again feature and now costs 2/2/2</li>\r\n	<li>Guard tower gives only +7 wall instead of 8</li>\r\n	<li>Phantom lancer - enemy gems: -3, instead of -4</li>\r\n	<li>Saint-day gives Stock: +3, instead of +5</li>\r\n	<li>Tax now costs 5/5/5 and is an Uncommon card</li>\r\n	<li>Knight attack lowered by 1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Uncommon cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Academy of destruction gives Stock: +2 and summons <b>Destruction</b> spells</li>\r\n	<li>Academy of illusion gives Stock: +2 and summons <b>Illusion spells</b></li>\r\n	<li>Basilisk attack raised by 1</li>\r\n	<li>Earth eater now can have maximum attack 23 and if his attack is higher then 15, he will not take all of enemy Bricks, but only so many as was his attack power</li>\r\n	<li>Enforcer attack is now the difference between en