d by 5G and 5R</li>\r\n	<li>Phoenix cost lowered by 4G, and rebirth is now triggered when his attack is higher than 30. Rebirth itself now gives +16 Gems when triggered</li>\r\n	<li>Valhalla won''t lower your tower below 1</li>\r\n	<li>Necromancer now summons a non-Rare <b>undead</b> cards</li>\r\n	<li>Mana burn cost raised to 27G</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>New keywords</h3>\r\n<h4>Holy</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Chapel</li>\r\n	<li>Fairy</li>\r\n	<li>Paladin</li>\r\n	<li>Heavenly warrior</li>\r\n	<li>Gift from the heavens</li>\r\n	<li>Cathedral</li>\r\n	<li>Seraphim</li>\r\n	<li>Angel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Soldier</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Archer</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy infantry</li>\r\n	<li>Knight</li>\r\n	<li>Lady Ellena</li>\r\n	<li>Swordsman</li>\r\n	<li>Light cavalry</li>\r\n	<li>Ceremonial guard</li>\r\n	<li>Dragon knights</li>\r\n	<li>Royal pikemen</li>\r\n	<li>Tower guards</li>\r\n	<li>Tyran''s pride</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Nature</h4>\r\n<ul> 		\r\n	<li>Erosion</li>\r\n	<li>Tremors</li>\r\n	<li>Blizzard</li>\r\n	<li>Flood</li>\r\n	<li>Telekinesis</li>\r\n	<li>Earthquake</li>\r\n	<li>Volcano</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Restoration</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Alchemy</li>\r\n	<li>Conjure bricks</li>\r\n	<li>Magical steel</li>\r\n	<li>Meditation</li>\r\n	<li>Restoration</li>\r\n	<li>Archangel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Destruction</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bloody moon</li>\r\n	<li>Cold arrow</li>\r\n	<li>Immolation</li>\r\n	<li>Lightning strike</li>\r\n	<li>Mystic strike</li>\r\n	<li>All-elemental attack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Illusion</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Corrosion</li>\r\n	<li>Mind control</li>\r\n	<li>Curse</li>\r\n	<li>Mirror strike</li>\r\n	<li>Sorrow</li>\r\n	<li>Duplication</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Charge</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Centaur patrol troop - 1</li>\r\n	<li>Knight - 3</li>\r\n	<li>Unicorn - 2</li>\r\n	<li>Light cavalry - 6</li>\r\n	<li>Dragon knights - 9</li> 		\r\n	<li>Pegasus - 4</li> 		\r\n	<li>Undead host - 15</li> 		\r\n	<li>Valkyrie - 5</li> 		\r\n	<li>Daemon - 8</li>\r\n</ul>'