costs 12B 8G</li>\r\n<li>Dragon knights have attack reduced to 33, but charge damage increased to 12</li>\r\n<li>Ent cost reduced by 1G</li>\r\n<li>Light cavalry attack reduced to 16, but charge damage increased to 9</li>\r\n<li>Lost city now costs 15B 6G</li>\r\n<li>Mind control cost raised to 26G</li>\r\n<li>Nightmare cost raised to 14/14, attack reduced to 20, but charge damage increased to 10</li>\r\n<li>Obsidian gargoyle condition changed from 3 to 5</li>\r\n<li>Pirates attack reduced by 1</li>\r\n<li>Treacherous artifact cost reduced to 11/11/11</li>\r\n<li>Valkyrie cost increased to 12R, attack lowered to 15, but charge damage increased to 7</li>\r\n<li>Work overtime gives wall+ 38 instead of 40</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Rare cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Angel cost lowered to 8G</li>\r\n<li>Black dragon cost raised by 3R, but now gives -15 enemy recruits (instead of 10)</li>\r\n<li>Daemon cost raised to 11/11</li>\r\n<li>Crugg cost lowered to 26R</li>\r\n<li>Elven reinforcemets reworked - it gives different cards</li>\r\n<li>Forced labour now gives +85 wall</li>\r\n<li>Luna attack raised by 5</li>\r\n<li>Necropolis reworked - it gives different cards and also gives less gems and recruits (5 instead of 10)</li>\r\n<li>Architectural improvment reworked - it gives different cards</li>\r\n<li>Generals army reworked - it gives different cards</li>\r\n<li>Vampire lord gives now only 5 gems instead of 15</li>\r\n<li>Word of power cost reduced by 3G</li>\r\n</ul>'),
('modified', '2007-11-26 00:00:00', '', '<h3>Common cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Acolyte gives Gems: +7 instead of +6</li>\r\n	<li>Avenger is now a <b>Holy</b> card and gives Recruits: +7 instead of +6</li>\r\n	<li>Black market reworked. Now targets only one card randomly chosen. Cost reduced to 3/3/3</li>\r\n	<li>Double wall cost reduced to 6 Bricks</li>\r\n	<li>Elf attack raised to 3</li>\r\n	<li>Forest hunter attack raised to 5, but now has enemy stock: -2</li>\r\n	<li>Guard tower	in Mode1 gives Wall: +8 instead of +7</li>\r\n	<li>Lookout towers now use primary effect only when having Tower &lt; 45</li>\r\n	<li>Magic lamp cost reduced to 5/5/5</li>\r\n	<li>Magic well secondary effect raised to Gems: +11 instead of +10</li>\r\n	<li>Militia cost raised to 5/5/5</li>\r\n	<li>Mithril mine secondary effect raised to Bricks: +12 instead of +11</li>\r\n	<li>Phantom lancer is now a <b>Brigand</b></li>\r\n	<li>Preparations secondary effect raised to Recruits: +11 instead of +10</li>\r\n	<li>Reinforced wall has new image</li>\r\n	<li>Speed renamed to Haste</li>\r\n	<li>Stone archer gives now Stock: +1 instead of Gems: +1</li>\r\n	<li>Stone atronarch gives now Bricks: +8 instead of +7</li>\r\n	<li>Stone golem in Mode2 Enemy wall: -9 instead of -8</li>\r\n	<li>Temple of light gives tower +3 instead of +5</li>\r\n	<li>Thieves with honor now cost 1R, has attack 8 and gives enemy stock: +2</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s left arm cost reduced to 8 bricks</li>\r\n	<li>Tribute reworked. Now targets only one card randomly chosen.</li>\r\n	<li>Undead raid cost raised to 4 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Wealth now gives stock: +7, but also enemy stock: +10</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Uncommon cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Assassins is now a <b>Brigand</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Balistae now cost 8 bricks and 8 recruits, but gives only Wall: +24</li>\r\n	<li>Banshee	attack raised to 4N + 4</li>\r\n	<li>Bloody moon cost raised to 12 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Border fortress cost reduced to 42 bricks</li>\r\n	<li>Cathedral now gives Tower: +13</li>\r\n	<li>Clay Golem in Mode1 attack raised to 25</li>\r\n	<li>Cold arrow attack raised to 8, but now takes only enemy gems: -6</li>\r\n	<li>Dwarven fortification cost reduced to 31 bricks, but now gives only Wall: +43</li>\r\n	<li>Elf enchantress attack raised to 9</li>\r\n	<li>Fairy dragon reworked. Now transfers all dragon from enemy hand to yours to matching positions, if there are none stock + 5</li>\r\n	<li>Fallen angel cost raised to 10 gems and 13 recruits, but now has Enemy stock: -N, N = #Holy cards in Enemy hand /2(rounded up)</li>\r\n	<li>Fallen knight attack raised by 3 and no longer has Production X0</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy cavalry has now new image (rotated)</li>\r\n	<li>Immolation cost raised to 13 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Invisible squad enemy tower: -9, instead of -8</li>\r\n	<li>Iron Golem attack riased to 21</li>\r\n	<li>Jealousy now cost 13 gems, but is more powerfull. If Tower &lt; 50 and Enemy tower &gt; 60 Enemy tower: -25 else Enemy tower: -10</li>\r\n	<li>Knight of time attack reduced by 1 and now is a <b>Mage</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Last hope secondary effect now gives Stock: +3</li>\r\n	<li>Lightning strike cost raised to 11 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Lost city now cost 15 bricks and 7 gems, but gives Tower: +5</li>\r\n	<li>Magical tower cost raised to 16 bricks</li>\r\n	<li>Monestery gives now Tower: +12 instead of +10</li>\r\n	<li>Mud elemental limit raised to 5 from 4</li>\r\n	<li>Murderer is now a <b>Brigand</b>, but cost raised to 18 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Obsidian gargoyle attack raised to 13 and condition If #Unliving cards in your hand &gt; 4 instead of &gt; 5</li>\r\n	<li>Orc regiment cost raised to 60R, but attack raised to 100</li>\r\n	<li>Pirates  attack raised to 12</li>\r\n	<li>Rock elemental limit raised to 5 from 4</li>\r\n	<li>Sabotage tunnel now has Enemy bricks: -10 and Enemy recruits: -10</li>\r\n	<li>Sacrifice cost raised to 5 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Sea monster now has Enemy bricks: -8 and Enemy recruits: -8 instead of -5/-5</li>\r\n	<li>Sorceress cost raised to 8 gems, base attack lowered to 6</li>\r\n	<li>Telekinesis cost reduced by 1G</li>\r\n	<li>Thievery cost reduced to 13 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Tidal wave cost riased to 17 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Time warp cost raised to 11 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s head condition lowered to 4 from 5</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s heart condition lowered to 4 from 5</li>\r\n	<li>Undead host reworked. It no longer has <b>Charge</b>. It''s attack chnged to 40 + 8N, N = #undead cards in hand</li>\r\n	<li>Valkyrie cost raised to 14 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Vampire cost raised to 17 gems, but now takes only Gems: -7, instead of -15</li>\r\n	<li>Vampire countess added an additional effect. If N &gt; 6 Magic: +1, N is #Undead cards in your hand</li>\r\n	<li>Warlord''s keep cost lowered by 4B</li>\r\n	<li>Wolf raiders cost reduced by 6R</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Rare cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Archmage now takes Enemy stock: -7 instead of -5</li>\r\n	<li>Avalanche is now more powerfull. Enemy tower: -8 and Enemy wall: -8 instead of -7/-7</li>\r\n	<li>Centaur trainer cost raised to 13 gems and 17 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Clay fabric cost raised to 11 gems and 11 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Daemon cost riased to 13 gems and 13 recruits, but Charge increased to 10</li>\r\n	<li>Dragon golem in Mode2 now gives Wall: +60 instead of +55 and now has Mode3:	Enemy wall: -70</li>\r\n	<li>Force labour now gives +105 wall instead of +85</li>\r\n	<li>General''s army reworked. Discards your hand and receive Archer, Heavy Infantry, Knight, Crusader, Royal pikemen, Light cavalry, Heavy cavalry, and Dragon knights, Recruits: +15</li>\r\n	<li>Implosion cost raised to 45 gems and 25 recruits</li>\r\n	<li>Magic barrier cost lowered to 25 bricks and 10 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Magic rift now cost 21 gems, and has Enemy gems: -15 and Enemy recruits: -10</li>\r\n	<li>Master of past reworked. Now negates effect of opponents last played card (effect only game attributes)</li>\r\n	<li>Micramix cost lowered to 10/10/10</li>\r\n	<li>Necropolis reworkd. Discards your hand and receive Zombie, Skeleton warriors, Ghoul, Stalker, Banshee, Emissary, Vampire, and Vampire countess.</li>\r\n	<li>Plan of salvation reworked. Discards your hand and receive Basic wall, two Fortified walls, two Double walls, Fortification, Great wall, and Border fortress.</li>\r\n	<li>Return to the beginning cost reduced to 20 bricks and 20 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Stonehenge cost reduced to 17 bricks and 13 gems</li>\r\n	<li>Tyran''s pride reworked. It is no longes <b>Soldier</b>. Completely new effect.</li>\r\n	<li>Vampire lord cost changed to 10 gems and 20 recruits. Attack raised to 25, now gives no additional gems</li>\r\n	<li>Wonder cost raised to 15 gems</li>\r\n</ul>');
