('modified', '2008-01-30 00:00:00', '', '<h3>Common cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Black market now costs 0 and switches two card instead of one</li>\r\n	<li>Conjurer cost reduced to 1G and now has Production X0</li>\r\n	<li>Necromancy is now a <b>Quick</b> card and costs 1G</li>\r\n	<li>Retribution cost lowered to 1G</li>\r\n	<li>Tribute now costs 0 and discards two cards instead of one</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Uncommon cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Auxilia cost lowered by one of each resource</li>\r\n	<li>Clay golem now has a third mode - enemy wall: -35</li>\r\n	<li>Basilisk attack lowered by 1</li>\r\n	<li>Fallen angel takes enemy stock -N instead of N / 2 (4 max), also attack increased by N</li>\r\n	<li>Last hope is now a <b>Quick</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Moonlight unicorn is now a <b>Swift</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Pegasus is now a <b>Quick</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Reserve forces attack increased by 3</li>\r\n	<li>Tax now costs 0</li>\r\n	<li>Warlord takes -17 enemy wall instead of -12</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Rare cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Demolition troop takes enemy wall -100 instead of -80</li>\r\n	<li>Luna the sorceress cost lowered to 25G</li>\r\n	<li>Prince of thieves has now upper limit to stealing - 20 of each resource</li>\r\n	<li>Completion ritual card text modified (instant destruction victory)</li>\r\n	<li>Return to beggining cost lowered to 10B 10G</li>\r\n	<li>Vamipre lord is now a <b>Quick</b> card</li>\r\n</ul>'),
('modified', '2008-07-30 20:49:30', '', '<h3>Common cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Caravan gives now extra 1 stock, when opponent lowered your stock last turn</li>\r\n	<li>Cleansing now chooses random undead cards</li>\r\n	<li>Erosion cost +1G</li>\r\n	<li>Golden scepter now costs 1/1/1</li>\r\n	<li>Retribution reworked - now reduces both players'' stock by one for each <b>Undead</b> in respective player''s hand (max 4)</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s left arm cost reduced by 1B</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s right arm cost reduced by 1B</li>\r\n	<li>Wind reduces enemy wall by 1 instead of 2, takes only one random resource from the opponent instead of whole 1 stock</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Uncommon cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Balistae reworked - cost 15B 15R, gives 30 wall and if there is a <b>Soldier</b> card in hand enemy tower is lowered by 11</li>\r\n	<li>Basilisk has a new picture</li>\r\n	<li>Cold arrow cost reduced by 2G, and takes 8 enemy gems, instead of 6</li>\r\n	<li>Crypt now summons non-common <b>Undead</b> instead of non-rare, gives no additional stock</li>\r\n	<li>Dragon egg cost reduced to 12G</li>\r\n	<li>Emissary of the Afterlife now replaces all cards not just non <b>Undead</b> ones, also the card positions are randomly chosen</li>\r\n	<li>Ethernal guardian cost reduced to 1/1/1</li>\r\n	<li>Fairy dragon gives now stock +6 instead of +5</li>\r\n	<li>Foundry cost reduced by 1B and gives tower +5 instead of +4</li>\r\n	<li>Glacial temple cost reduced to zero</li>\r\n	<li>Gladiator now has "next card will be a non-common <b>Barbarian</b>" feature</li>\r\n	<li>Last hope gives stock +2 instead of stock +3</li>\r\n	<li>Lich now summons <b>Undead</b> card of the same rarity as was the card he discarded</li>\r\n	<li>Meditation reworked - cost 15G and gives 25G, if last card was a <b>Mage</b> you get bonus 8G</li>\r\n	<li>Mirror strike card effect text corrected</li>\r\n	<li>Necromancy amplifier reworked - now upgrades your <b>Undead</b> cards (Common->Uncommon, Uncommon->Rare (max 1 Rare)) and also cost raised by 1/1/1</li>\r\n	<li>Ninja reworked - it''s no longer a <b>Brigand</b>, has enemy tower -2 and stock -1, also it is now a <b>Durable</b> card</li>\r\n	<li>Samurai reworked - it''s no longer a Barbarian, discards one random card from enemy hand, that has a keyword. You get cost of the discarded card (max 5)</li>\r\n	<li>Sand worm lowers enemy wall by 19 instead of 18 and enemy tower by 16 instead of 15</li>\r\n	<li>Sorceres outpost condition changed - "if there is a <b>Legend</b> card in hand" instead of "if #<b>Mage</b> cards in hand > 4"</li>\r\n	<li>Tartarus gate cost lowered to 4/4/4 and now summons a non-common <b>Titan</b></li>\r\n	<li>Time lock cost reduced by 2G</li>\r\n	<li>Unholy shrine has now ability to select one card from hand that will not be discarded by its effect, also it now chooses the cards that will be discarded at random</li>\r\n	<li>Warchief has wall +15 instead of +10, also card text has been corrected</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Rare cards</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Completion ritual has no longer the "else" effect</li>\r\n	<li>Generals army reworked - now costs 20R instead od 0, gives 35R instead of 15R, also archer summon has been replaced by Light infantry and Heavy cavalry summon has been replaced by Battle formations</li>\r\n	<li>Master of past corrected - it no longer negates effect of your previous played card, when played after <b>Quick</b> or <b>Swift</b> card. It has no effect in this case, so don''t play it after <b>Quick</b> or <b>Swift</b> card!</li>\r\n	<li>Necromancer now summons non-common cards instead of non-rare</li>\r\n	<li>Necropolis cost raised to 13/13/13, it gives no additional stock</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>New keywords</h3>\r\n<h4>Alliance</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dwarven miners</li>\r\n	<li>Dwarven warriors</li>\r\n	<li>Elf</li>\r\n	<li>Elite elf</li>\r\n	<li>Elven archer</li>\r\n	<li>Giant bear</li>\r\n	<li>Dwarven fortification</li>\r\n	<li>Elf commando</li>\r\n	<li>Elf enchatress</li>\r\n	<li>Ent</li>\r\n	<li>Griffin</li>\r\n	<li>Roc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Banish</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ogre</li>\r\n	<li>Werewolf</li>\r\n	<li>Paladin</li>\r\n	<li>Sea monster</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Legend</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Azure unicorn</li>\r\n	<li>Moonlight unicorn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Skirmisher</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Amazon</li>\r\n	<li>Minotaur</li>\r\n	<li>Royal pikeman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Titan</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Titan''s left arm</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s right arm</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s head</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s heart</li>\r\n	<li>Titan''s legs</li>\r\n	<li>Completion ritual</li>\r\n</ul>');
